<p>Hi <strong style="color:#F0F0F0;">{{fullName}}</strong>,</p>
<p>
  Use the one-time code below to verify your email address.
  The code expires in <strong style="color:#F0F0F0;">{{expiresMins}} minutes</strong>.
</p>

<div class="otp-box">
  <div class="otp-code">{{otp}}</div>
